name: Danny Connors & The Ladders E.P.
description:
Debut E.P. featuring tracks by Danny Connors & The Ladders;

1/ If You Could See
2/ Temperature
3/ We Can Have It
4/ This Is My Heart
5/ I Will Be At Home

All songs and arrangements by Danny Connors (Lead Vocals / Guitar) Joe Kenny (Lead Vocals / Guitar) Lee Canham (Lead Vocals / Bass) Greg Coulson (Vocals / Keys) and Dan Benton (Drums)
